 đưa Tiểu Viễn ra nước ngoài. Đến lúc này, anh chợt cảm thấy dường như mình đã thiếu mất thứ gì đó. Cuối cùng, hai con người không mang quan hệ huyết thống chỉ có thể là người nhà, là anh em thôi ư? Hay họ vẫn có cơ hội vượt qua ranh giới cấm đoán, trở thành tình nhân?","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"243069","season":1,"vote_average":8.4,"vote_count":20},"modified":"2024-05-04T20:02:00.000Z","cast":["Chris Chiu","Kurt Huang","Tammy Lin","Jae-Hoon Kim","Danny Liang","Yankee Yang","Sam Lin","Justin Chang","Alisia Liang","Linda Lin","Prince Chiu","Max Kuo","Ruan Bo-hao"],"director":["Jui-Chih Chiang"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Chris Chiu","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Chris Chiu","tmdb_id":2259652,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nYul7Kc6hTYo3SaYdKTTGm3HK8U.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2259652"},{"name":"Kurt Huang","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kurt Huang","tmdb_id":4342791,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pu0VVNSQuzaJfuyzPSm3T9gTnA6.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/4342791"},{"name":"Tammy Lin","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Tammy Lin","tmdb_id":3185102,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/q6rMfOYnCn2geuO1ThoRb2zPx1O.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3185102"},{"name":"Jae-Hoon Kim","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Jae-Hoon Kim","tmdb_id":3741703,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iAU3HPYGvFdpWDXeCa7k1l436rR.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3741703"},{"name":"Danny Liang","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Danny Liang","tmdb_id":581796,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sZ15L5kaFIOWUDitR1YfYuqrdDH.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/581796"},{"name":"Yankee Yang","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Yankee Yang","tmdb_id":2039031,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/v6RCP8jgumaJ2bgYAf0omgzIHSx.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2039031"},{"name":"Sam Lin","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Sam Lin","tmdb_id":2182908,"profile":"http